            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#nichthauserF" start="435.730" end="x">He worked on the street with a shovel. Because the Germans demanded it. All men had to work on the street and the Jewish girls were taken to scrub floors and to wash windows.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="451.555" end="x">For whom?</span>
        </li>
